(221, 'Generation Google, Google Lime, Women Techmakers Scholarships', '', '<em>The three scholarships below are for computer science majors and related degrees (this includes ECE, CE, and Data Analytics).</em><br><ul><br><li><br><strong><a href="http://ohio-state.us11.list-manage.com/track/click?u=9984bd1eae9eb3104355b9c94&amp;id=a6658246db&amp;e=bb0af33337" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">Women Techmakers Scholars Program</a></strong> (formerly known as the Google Anita Borg Memorial Scholarship) is open to current female undergraduate or graduate students who will be studying at a university in the United States or Canada for the 2017-2018 academic year. <strong>Deadline: December 1, 2016</strong><br></li><br><li><br><strong><a href="http://ohio-state.us11.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=9984bd1eae9eb3104355b9c94&amp;id=88ac5847b9&amp;e=bb0af33337" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">Generation Google Scholarship</a></strong> is open to current undergraduate or graduate students from an underrepresented background in computer science who will be studying at a university in United States or Canada for the 2017-2018 academic year.  <strong>Deadline: December 1, 2016</strong><br></li><br><li><br><strong><a href="http://ohio-state.us11.list-manage.com/track/click?u=9984bd1eae9eb3104355b9c94&amp;id=44cd14b247&amp;e=bb0af33337" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">Google Lime Scholarship</a></strong> is open to current undergraduate or graduate students with disabilities who will be studying at a university in United States or Canada for the 2017-2018 academic year. <strong> Deadline: December 4, 2016</strong><br></li><br></ul>', 'teamup', '2193528', '2016-10-31T00:00:00', '2016-10-31T23:59:00', 2, 0),
(215, 'OUABringing Home The Gold with Kayla Harrison', 'Ohio Union Performance Hall', 'OUAB is hosting 2016 Rio Gold Medalist &amp; Olympian in the sport of Judo, Kayla Harrison. Tickets are free, two per BuckID and are available at the Ohio Union Information Desk.<br> ', 'teamup', '836635', '2016-10-27T19:00:00', '2016-10-27T21:30:00', 2, 0),
(214, 'The Plough and the Stars', 'Southern Theater downtown', 'Open exclusively to Ohio State students at a special price of $10 per ticket.  <br><strong>The iconic Irish play,</strong> “The Plough and the Stars” is co-presented by The Ohio State University’s College of Arts and Sciences and the Columbus Association for the Performing Arts (CAPA) in honor of the 100th Anniversary of Ireland’s Easter Rising. Set amid the tumult of the Easter Rising, The Plough and the Stars is the story of ordinary lives ripped apart by the idealism of the time. The residents of a Dublin tenement shelter from the violence that sweeps through the city''s streets. A revolution that will shape the country''s future rages around them. What kind of Ireland awaits them? The Plough and the Stars was first performed at the Abbey Theatre in 1926. The audience rioted. Now regarded as a masterpiece, this provocative play is an essential part of our understanding of 1916. Olivier Award-winning director Sean Holmes brings a new perspective to Sean O''Casey''s absorbing play produced by Ireland’s own Abbey Theatre.<em><br></em><br><em>To attend, RSVP <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSepe7doUkwNV66lvrVD7dE4j8Y5PgBaHOWAdXsYGjqC_LcABA/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">here</a>. Meet at the Ohio Union Bus Turnaround at 4:15pm to board the bus.</em>', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-27T17:00:00', '2016-10-27T19:30:00', 2, 0),
(213, 'Big Data Law and Policy', 'Drinko Hall’s Saxbe Auditorium ', '<em>Event will be interesting for all STEM majors, and specifically helpful for students in Engineering, Techonology and Mathematics</em><br>Employing increasingly sophisticated algorithms and artificial intelligence technologies, businesses and governments are enthusiastically using big data to solve problems and create value. At the same time, individuals are increasingly worried about how massive data collection and analysis will impact their privacy, and whether companies and governments will use it fairly. <strong>Do we need ground rules to encourage the many benefits, and reduce the risks, of our new algorithmic society?</strong> If so, can government set such rules consistent with the First Amendment?<br>To register, click <a href="http://moritzlaw.osu.edu/registrations/event/sidley-austin-distinguished-lecture/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">here</a>.', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-27T16:00:00', '2016-10-27T18:00:00', 2, 0),
(212, '2016 Health Sciences Majors Fair', 'Biomedical Research Tower, Room 115', '<em>For students interested in health sciences</em><br> <br>Meet representatives from the following (see below) health care-focused<strong> undergraduate and graduate/professional programs</strong>. To register, please click <a href="http://scarletandgray.osu.edu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">here</a>. and enter the access code “Health2016.”<br> <br>Applied Clinical and Preclinical Research <br>Athletic Training <br>Biomedical Science <br>Biophysics<br>Dental Hygiene<br>Dentistry <br>Health and Wellness Innovation in Health Care<br>Health Information<br>Management and Systems<br>Health Sciences <br>Law <br>Medical Dietetics <br>Medical Laboratory<br>Science <br>Medical Scientist Training Program <br>Medicine <br>Neuroscience <br>Nursing <br>Occupational<br>Therapy <br>Optometry <br>Pharmacy <br>Physical Therapy <br>Public Health <br>Radiologic Sciences and<br>Therapy <br>Respiratory Therapy <br>Social Work <br>University Exploration <br>Veterinary Medicine<br>UAP170020', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-27T15:00:00', '2016-10-27T17:00:00', 2, 0),
(211, 'Wellness Workshop: Managing Relationships', 'Ohio Union, Barbie Tootle Room', 'Healthy relationships will be defined, stages of a relationship will be discussed, as well as role playing on ways to deal with differences and power struggles in a relationship. Participants will determine various issues that arise in relationships (i.e. jealousy) and working with the facilitator to think through these issues and options students may have in the particular situations. Lastly, we will be discussing how to maintain a healthy relationship.', 'teamup', '836635', '2016-10-27T12:00:00', '2016-10-27T13:00:00', 2, 0),
(210, 'Pre-Health Collegium Speaker', 'Hagerty 071', 'The Pre-Health Collegium will be hosting Dr. William Miller this Wednesday, October 26, at 6:30 pm. Dr. Miller, MD, PhD, MPH, is the current Chair of the College of Public Health and will be speaking about career options within medicine, experiences within his own career, and will be open for Q&amp;A. <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSekDEtgryCrFclQp_y3lVY_sOgqBOugbOFpMVvbRxI7Fh8pFA/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">RSVP preferred</a> but walk ins welcome!', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-26T18:30:00', '2016-10-26T19:30:00', 2, 0),
(209, ' Flicks for Free ft. The Conjuring 2', 'Ohio Union, U.S. Bank Conference Theater', '<em>Free popcorn and beverages will be provided</em><br>In 1977, paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren travel to London, England, where single mother Peggy Hodgson believes that something evil is in her home. When Peggy''s youngest daughter starts showing signs of demonic possession, Ed and Lorraine attempt to help the besieged girl, only to find themselves targeted by the malicious spirits.<br> ', 'teamup', '836635', '2016-10-26T18:00:00', '2016-10-26T20:00:00', 2, 0),
(208, 'Coding Workshop: Introduction to Swift for iOS', 'OSU TechHub', '"Have you ever wanted to code for iOS but didn’t know quite where to start? As <a href="http://hack.osu.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">Hack OHI/O</a> approaches we thought this would be a great opportunity to have one of our friends from Apple® visit and provide and introduction to Swift™ and X code®. This interactive workshop will go over the basics of creating an app for iPhone® or iPad®. It will occur in store on October 26 from 6:00- 8:00 p.m."<br>See <a href="https://techhub.osu.edu/news/2016/10/06/coding-workshop-introduction-swift-ios" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">here</a> for more details. <a href="https://osu.az1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_3s1febZu43NEgw5" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">RSVP</a> reqiured.', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-26T18:00:00', '2016-10-26T20:00:00', 2, 0);
