(178, 'Graduate Engineering Open House', 'The Blackwell Inn and Conference Center', '<em>For students in Engineering</em><br> <br>The Graduate Engineering Open House functions as a<strong> graduate program preview f</strong>or prospective students at The Ohio State University’s Columbus campus. This is a two-day event  and provides an opportunity to learn about what College of Engineering has to offer you as a graduate student.<br> <br>To RSVP, click <a href="https://engineering.osu.edu/events/2016/10/graduate-engineering-open-house" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">here</a>.', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-14T08:00:00', '2016-10-15T15:00:00', 2, 0),
