(164, 'Society of Women Engineers Cardinal Health Tour', 'Cardinal Health', 'Society of Women Engineers (SWE) is hosting a Cardinal Health Tour. This event is highly recommended for women in engineering of any year.  <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc51rMjOg0fFAT9UQBKSU19SM2o-Vu43_34izy3uBJoYvVYeA/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener external">RSVP was required for this event.</a>', 'teamup', '2155517', '2016-10-07T13:30:00', '2016-10-07T16:00:00', 2, 0),
